{"tid":1441034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載] 香港學生罷課聯盟-9月份中學生罷課","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T08:09:03.000Z","uid":296535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"296e679769b1c94c01091c8080ca7f88e3ca3159","tid":1441034,"uid":296535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkaQhnt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkaQhnt.jpg&h=bcd7b6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盡早廣傳 已核實</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要由頭睇到落尾</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【九月罷課 學生自決】<br />\n<br />\n六七八月，香港風起，然今煙淚未散而存。過去，中學生發起學生聯署反對送中惡法，甚至以身把淚血拼煙雲，仍是未能得到合理之回應。暑假已臨暮昏，惜送中惡法危機仍存，警、政、民關係更是未嘗得治。開學之日即將上演，我等中學生不能坐以待斃，必須繼續堅持心中的理想，無計可施下，以罷課凝聚中學生力量，讓政府明白，我等非枉讀之輩，稍懂筆墨亦同存良心，敢於環看政治。<br />\n<br />\n雖未讀盡萬卷書，但我等亦願走萬里路，為香港，萬里路比起萬卷書，何重何輕？<br />\n<br />\n故就罷課事宜，香港各大中學生組織包括中學時政、青年前線、悉政學揚、學生動源及學生抗命力量將成立聯盟，名曰香港學生罷課聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n望能因此喚醒中學生對政治觸覺，讓中學生行使公民責任，勇於發聲，向政府證明中學生力量。同時提升中學生對反修例運動參與度。<br />\n<br />\n蔽盟歡迎各學生組織加入聯盟，僅此望各界支援學生大罷課！<br />\n<br />\n鈞鑒<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟創始組織<br />\n中學時政<br />\n青年前線<br />\n悉政學揚<br />\n學生動源<br />\n學生抗爭力量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月10日<br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟Facebook Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongStudentStrikeAlliance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongStudentStrikeAlliance%2F&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=35cda437\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongStudentStrikeAlliance/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟Instagram Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/studentstrikesept?igshid=14lh92elzufd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstudentstrikesept%3Figshid%3D14lh92elzufd0&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=51a63037\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/studentstrikesept?igshid=14lh92elzufd0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟Telegram Channel <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkongstudentstrikealliance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongstudentstrikealliance&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=ba59754f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkongstudentstrikealliance</a>"},{"pid":"4825218c0353a0be5d6bf64dbccc76e1fc00648b","tid":1441034,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5856748c400fd2f057cbe8a13980b377c8bb8edd","tid":1441034,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:04:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff2a896c4b7cdb8ad10ca839fca7f9c99cc5e6ef","tid":1441034,"uid":293036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:09:03.000Z","msg":"唔好搞到好似佔中果時咁就得"}]}